data.description:
**Contingent upon bank approved short sale**This is 5496 Sandusky Road. With a total of 4 lots coming together to make 3/4 of an acre, there is plenty of yard space to entertain just about any amount of company you'd like to invite over. When you're not entertaining, you may want to share that space occasionally as you watch from your deck, the nearby deer frolicking through your yard.
This split level ranch allots you over 2300 sq. ft. offers plenty of room inside too including 5 bedrooms (3 up, 2 down), 2 full bathrooms and 2 living spaces. Your vehicles will be happy also nestled in the spacious attached 2 car garage. Located in Bath school district, this home will absolutely not last. 
Open house will be held 10/10/23 from 5 until 7 PM. **Note: Kitchen refrigerator is NOT included in the sale.
